description:
"I think I'm going to actually take this young man," Alan said, referring to Keith who was sitting next to him. "He's been gone for a while and we're going to work him over today!"

"I'm ready," Keith said. "I'm excited."

They both had big smiles on their faces.

I hadn't seen Keith in a while. He was looking cute as ever, with his sparkling blue eyes. The only difference was that he had put on a little more muscle and his shoulder tattoo had gotten bigger.

The two of them had an incredible fuck session. As for the ending, it could be called "Fun With Cum!"
title: Keith & Alan
